column5: Does anyone know of any lakes around Haliburton or Bancroft area for Crappie?  Thanks Court
Just saw on another site that someone caught some in Kash.  There were pictures to support it also, so there you go.  What the heck do I know.
Ive heard the exist on Kash but targeting them and catching them is another story. Big lake for the area
try fishing for them on kashag, right near the bridge in ingolsby were the lake enters canning. a guy from the fisheries in haliburton told me that were you will catch them.
